question: What are the titles for papers whose topic is related to AI and publication year is later than 2018?
sub_query: Titles of papers related to AI
document_path: https://zhujuneray.github.io/assets/provenance/data/paper/raw_data/A Lived Informatics Model of Personal Informatics.pdf
final_answer: The titles for papers related to AI and published after 2018 are "HeartLink: Open Broadcast of Live Biometric Data to Social Networks," "Are your Participants Gaming the System? Screening Mechanical Turk Workers," and "Persuasive Technology in the Real World: A Study of Long-Term Use of Activity Sensing Devices for Fitness."
sub_answers: Titles of papers related to AI include "HeartLink: Open Broadcast of Live Biometric Data to Social Networks," "Are your Participants Gaming the System? Screening Mechanical Turk Workers," and "Persuasive Technology in the Real World: A Study of Long-Term Use of Activity Sensing Devices for Fitness."
I don't have the information regarding the publication year of papers after 2018.
